M|rules|title: Use Activity Component for Show/Hide
M|rules|impact: MEDIUM
M|rules|impactDescription: preserves state/DOM
M|rules|tags: rendering, activity, visibility, state-preservation
M|rules|Use React's `<Activity>` to preserve state/DOM for expensive components that frequently toggle visibility.
M|rules|**Usage:**
M|rules|```tsx
M|rules|import { Activity } from 'react'
M|rules|function Dropdown({ isOpen }: Props) {
M|rules|return (
M|rules|<Activity mode={isOpen ? 'visible' : 'hidden'}>
M|rules|<ExpensiveMenu />
M|rules|</Activity>
M|rules|)
M|rules|}
M|rules|```
M|rules|Avoids expensive re-renders and state loss.